Date: Thu, 24 Jul 2025 14:25:46 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] monitor: alsa: Dont set 'node.dont-remix' property to
 loopback devices

This is really not needed and allows the ALSA loopback adapters to be configured
with any number of channels.
---
 src/scripts/monitors/alsa.lua | 1 -
 1 file changed, 1 deletion(-)

diff --git a/src/scripts/monitors/alsa.lua b/src/scripts/monitors/alsa.lua
index e0ee092d..7758807c 100644
--- a/src/scripts/monitors/alsa.lua
+++ b/src/scripts/monitors/alsa.lua
@@ -63,7 +63,6 @@ function CreateLoopback (properties)
     ["audio.channels"] = channels,
     ["audio.position"] = position,
     ["alsa.loopback"] = true,
-    ["stream.dont-remix"] = true,
     ["node.passive"] = true,
     ["node.dont-fallback"] = true,
     ["node.linger"] = true,
